name: Android Youtube Downloader
tagline: A small YouTube Downloader based on my extractor library
body: ## Extractor Library This page is about the downloader App if you are interested in the extractor library used by the App refer to the [github page](https://github.com/HaarigerHarald/android-youtubeExtractor). ## App The App basically consists of a dialog window, that is accessible through the "Share" option in your browser or within the YouTube App: [YouTube Downloader](https://github.com/HaarigerHarald/android-youtubeExtractor/releases/download/v1.0.0/youtubeDownloader.apk) ## Limitations * Private videos * Live streams * Audio is m4a (aac), no mp3 support
